{"tid":1716700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"篤爆沉默的藍絲品牌 (1) - 德善健髮","createTime":"2019-11-13T11:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:58:42.000Z","uid":325560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd40062a32da75059d7ced97d009b1e979810d6a","tid":1716700,"uid":325560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"仲係P牌，就算信唔信都好，都想講出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我做過幾間公司，都係藍絲老闆，只不過佢哋唔敢出聲。我唔想手足啲錢無端端洗左落去比呢啲仆街。所以逐一篤爆。第一間係<br />\n<br />\n一) 德善健髮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dshc.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dshc.com.hk%2F&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0Qm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=7fbd04ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dshc.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n而家仲係CCTVB日日賣廣告，用黃浩然做代言。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKtsn2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKtsn2s.jpg&h=d0a0b78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個老細其實係一個女中醫，叫做張琛，佢係十幾年前就出位，成日話同啲明星睇中醫，例如陳奕迅戒煙都搵佢之類；同埋成日帶住啲名牌，就係咁樣出左位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqAKqiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqAKqiQ.jpg&h=9696fc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢個人其實深藍都發黑，亦都鍾意請大陸人，例如佢身邊就有個擦鞋仔就係廣州人叫Andrew Lin，連森美對元朗721表態都話係好黃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆周不時都係WhatsApp嗰度，send一啲藍絲消息，又叫人投票支持藍絲立場之類。又話香港暴動，如果暴動仲係完唔到嘅話，就會大力發展大灣區咁話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6LN7uk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6LN7uk.png&h=e83e8346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，喺運動期間佢炒過一個同事，口講話表現唔到，實際上好多人都懷疑係因為個同事漏咗口風佢係黃。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個品牌嘅知名度而家都仲唔係好高，但係公司仲落緊廣告，唔想有啲唔知情嘅黃絲帶中咗「圈套」。所以要推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}